				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
<p>Parents and guardians can find announcements about Young Scholars closings and delays on local radio and TV stations: WPXI, WTAE, and KDKA. You can get up-to-the-minute school delay and closure information by receiving automated phone calls, texts, and/or emails from the Young Scholars message system, SchoolReach. You can also follow us on Facebook and Twitter.</p>
<p>Please note: School is canceled only during unusual circumstances such as extreme weather, facilities or equipment failure, an environmental hazard, or a public crisis that causes a significant safety risk. In the case of weather, Young Scholars considers mainly McKeesport Schools when scheduling delays and closings.</p>
